//[Reference] 'Oh! I...I didn't expect to see you here...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10000100=噢！我……我没想到会在这里见到你……
//[Reference] 'Uh... How did you even get here? Those devices are one time use and rather hard to make...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10000200=呃……你是怎么到这儿来的？那些设备是一次性的，而且很难制造……
//[Reference] 'It was that ^c:1486b0;scientist^c:pop;, wasn't it?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10000300=是那个^c:1486b0;科学家^c:pop;，对吧？
//[Reference] 'I just wanted to bring ^c:1486b0;Leif^c:pop; back, you know?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10000400=我只是想把^c:1486b0;雷夫^c:pop;带回来，你知道吗？
//[Reference] 'We all wanted that, but he just wouldn't come...kept talking about duty in his letters...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10000500=我们都希望这样，但是他不肯来……一直在信中说他的职责什么的……
//[Reference] 'It was really hard to build something that could transfer objects from place to place!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10000600=制造一个能把物体从一个地方传送到另一个地方的东西非常困难！
//[Reference] 'It was one-time-use too...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10000700=而且它还是一次性的……
//[Reference] 'How did she even fix it?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10000800=她是怎么把它修好的？
//[Reference] 'Well never mind. You're here now.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10000900=算了，现在你来了。
//[Reference] 'At least one of you came willingly...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10001000=至少你们之中有一个人自愿来了……
//[Reference] 'I'm here to bring ^c:1486b0;Leif^c:pop; back.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10001100=我来这里是要把^c:1486b0;雷夫^c:pop;带回去的。
//[Reference] 'Oh...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10001200=噢……
//[Reference] 'I shouldn't really help you, but...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10001300=我真的不该帮助你，可是……
//[Reference] 'It's hard to see him so distressed.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10001400=很难见到他如此沮丧。
//[Reference] 'Perhaps it was truly wrong of me to drag him back. Maybe he'll come back of his own free will someday...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10001500=也许强行把他带回来真的是我错了，或许有一天他会心甘情愿地回来的……
//[Reference] 'Alright. I'll help you. It won't be easy though...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10001600=好吧，我会帮你的，不过这可不容易……
//[Reference] 'We didn't want him to run away so we moved him somewhere...special...for the time being.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10001700=我们不想让他逃走，所以就把他暂时送到了一个……特殊的……地方。
//[Reference] 'If you could get me a few items I should be able to pull together something that will whisk you past the barrier.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10001800=如果你能给我带来几件物品，我应该就能制造出什么东西帮你越过障碍。
//[Reference] 'There should be ^c:d03e37;five components^c:pop;. If you look around the ^c:1486b0;tree houses^c:pop; here you should find them.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10001900=一共需要^c:d03e37;五个部件^c:pop;。你去^c:1486b0;树屋^c:pop;附近看看应该就能找到。
//[Reference] 'We shouldn't be seen talking until you find the ^c:d03e37;five components^c:pop;.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002000=等你找到^c:d03e37;五个部件^c:pop;之后再来吧。
//[Reference] 'It would be bad if they suspected something was happening...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002100=如果他们起了疑心就糟了……
//[Reference] 'Yes, this looks like everything we need!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002200=没错，我们需要的都在这儿了！
//[Reference] 'Now if you just give me a minu-'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002300=现在，请稍等一——
//[Reference] 'I apologise, the device initiated before I was quite ready.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002400=很抱歉，这个设备在我准备好之前就启动了。
//[Reference] 'I hope I didn't cause you too much unnecessary concern...?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002500=希望我没有给你造成不必要的困扰……？
//[Reference] 'That's great, we need to figure out where Tomti has taken ^c:1486b0;Maximilian^c:pop; and ^c:1486b0;Vorlen^c:pop;.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002510=太好了，我们得找到托蒂把^c:1486b0;马克西米利安^c:pop;还有^c:1486b0;沃伦^c:pop;带到哪里去了才行？
//[Reference] 'Could you take a look around the ^c:1486b0;Town Hall^c:pop; and the ^c:1486b0;Museum^c:pop;?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002511=你能去^c:1486b0;小镇大厅^c:pop;还有^c:1486b0;博物馆^c:pop;附近找找看吗？
//[Reference] 'There may be some clues there.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002520=那里可能会找到一些线索。
//[Reference] 'I understand that you're probably very busy right now.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002530=我知道你现在可能很忙。
//[Reference] 'But please come back soon. This town can't work without ^c:1486b0;Maximilian^c:pop; after all.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002540=但是请尽快回来。毕竟，这座小镇不能没有^c:1486b0;马克西米利安^c:pop;。
//[Reference] 'Oh! You managed to convince ^c:1486b0;Cecile^c:pop; to fix it?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002550=噢！你成功说服^c:1486b0;塞茜尔^c:pop;修好它了吗？
//[Reference] 'Is that the ^c:d03e37;teleporter^c:pop;? I don't trust that... but you should definitely use it.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002560=那是^c:d03e37;传送仪^c:pop;吗？虽然我不是很相信……但是你只能用它了。
//[Reference] 'I'm out of options anyway...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002570=反正我是没辙了……
//[Reference] 'I should have spent more time with ^c:1486b0;Tomti^c:pop;...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002580=我应该多花点时间陪陪^c:1486b0;托蒂^c:pop;的……
//[Reference] 'Ah, ^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;. I was just looking for you.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002590=啊，^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;。我正在找你呢。
//[Reference] 'Thank you so much for finding ^c:1486b0;Tomti^c:pop;!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002600=谢谢你找到了^c:1486b0;托蒂^c:pop;！
//[Reference] 'I hope he hasn't caused you much trouble.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002610=希望他没有给你惹太大的麻烦。
//[Reference] 'I just finished talking with him and he was in a much better mood.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002620=我刚跟他聊完，现在他心情好多了。
//[Reference] 'Judging by that, I doubt he'll be causing any more trouble...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002630=所以，我想他不会再惹什么麻烦了……
//[Reference] 'Not for the time being anyway.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002640=至少暂时不会了。
//[Reference] 'Well... I'll be going back to the ^c:1486b0;Treetop Village^c:pop; now.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002650=嗯……现在，我要回^c:1486b0;树顶村^c:pop;去了。
//[Reference] 'We'll keep ^c:1486b0;Tomti^c:pop; out of your hair for now.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002660=我们会让^c:1486b0;托蒂^c:pop;暂时别来打扰你的。
//[Reference] 'Hi ^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;! I was looking for you!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002670=嗨，^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;！我正找你呢！
//[Reference] 'I didn't expect to be back here after that previous... situation.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002680=我没想到在经历了上次的……情况后，我还能回到这里来。
//[Reference] 'I generally don't leave the ^c:1486b0;Treetop Village^c:pop;...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002690=一般我是不会离开^c:1486b0;树顶村^c:pop;的……
//[Reference] 'There is always someone to converse with, or construction to be done.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002700=总有人需要交谈，有建筑需要建造。
//[Reference] 'But there is a slight problem...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002710=但现在出了点小问题……
//[Reference] 'Remember that teleporter I used to bring ^c:1486b0;Leif^c:pop; home?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002720=还记得之前我用来带^c:1486b0;雷夫^c:pop;回家的传送仪吗？
//[Reference] 'Well, my brother ^c:1486b0;Tomti^c:pop; took it.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002730=那个，我弟弟^c:1486b0;托蒂^c:pop;把它拿走了。
//[Reference] 'We don't know where he could have gotten to... He hasn't been around for a while.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002740=我们都不知道他去了哪里……他有段时间没出现了。
//[Reference] 'We've all been so busy. And with ^c:1486b0;Leif^c:pop; not choosing not to stay...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002750=我们一直都很忙，再加上^c:1486b0;雷夫^c:pop;没有选择留下来……
//[Reference] 'Maybe he's just a bit lonely...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002760=可能他只是感觉有点孤独……
//[Reference] 'Sorry... lets get off that tangent for now.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002770=对不起……暂时别讨论这个话题了。
//[Reference] '^c:1486b0;Tomti^c:pop; has taken ^c:1486b0;Maximilian^c:pop; with him!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002780=^c:1486b0;托蒂^c:pop;带走了^c:1486b0;马克西米利安^c:pop;！
//[Reference] 'I think he may have taken ^c:1486b0;Vorlen^c:pop; as well.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002790=可能还有^c:1486b0;沃伦^c:pop;。
//[Reference] 'Can you help me look for clues?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002800=你能帮我找找线索吗？
//[Reference] 'Yes!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002810=好！
//[Reference] 'Not right now.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002820=现在不行。
//[Reference] 'Are you ready? We need to find ^c:1486b0;Tomti^c:pop;!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002830=你准备好了吗？我们得找到^c:1486b0;托蒂^c:pop;才行！
//[Reference] 'Yes!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002840=好！
//[Reference] 'Not right now.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002850=现在不行。
//[Reference] 'Have you managed to find any clues?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002860=你找到什么线索了吗？
//[Reference] 'Hopefully we can find something about their whereabouts...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002870=希望我们能找到他们的下落……
//[Reference] 'Could you take a look around the ^c:1486b0;Town Hall^c:pop; and the ^c:1486b0;Museum^c:pop;?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002880=你能去^c:1486b0;小镇大厅^c:pop;还有^c:1486b0;博物馆^c:pop;附近找找看吗？
//[Reference] 'You found something. Great!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002890=你找到什么了吗？太好了！
//[Reference] 'It looks like a ^c:d03e37;fragment^c:pop; of a ^c:d03e37;teleporter^c:pop;... maybe.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002900=看起来好像是……某个^c:d03e37;传送仪^c:pop;的碎片。
//[Reference] 'If you can find another ^c:d03e37;fragment^c:pop;, it might give us more to go on!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002910=如果你能找到另一块^c:d03e37;碎片^c:pop;，我们也许就能找到办法了！
//[Reference] 'Make sure to check around the ^c:1486b0;Town Hall^c:pop; and the ^c:1486b0;Museum^c:pop;?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002920=^c:1486b0;小镇大厅^c:pop;和^c:1486b0;博物馆^c:pop;附近都有好好找过了吗？
//[Reference] 'Great! Those look like parts of a ^c:d03e37;teleporter^c:pop;...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10002930=太好了！看样子像某个^c:d03e37;传送仪^c:pop;的零件……
//[Reference] 'They still look in decent condition.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10004800=不过好像还没坏掉。
//[Reference] 'Let me take those. I'll quickly assemble them back together...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10004900=交给我吧，我很快就能把它们组装起来……
//[Reference] 'I figured... since she managed last time...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10005000=搞定了……因为上次她就成功过……
//[Reference] 'I don't know how ^c:1486b0;Cecile^c:pop; did it... You may need to ask her to help.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10005100=不知道^c:1486b0;塞茜尔^c:pop;上次是怎么做到的……你可能需要去请她帮个忙。
//[Reference] 'I don't know how ^c:1486b0;Cecile^c:pop; managed to do it...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10005200=不知道^c:1486b0;塞茜尔^c:pop;上次是怎么做到的……
//[Reference] 'Go see her for me, I think she will help out.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10005300=帮我去问问她吧，我想她会帮忙的。
//[Reference] 'Nice meeting you ^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10005400=很高兴见到你，^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;！
//[Reference] 'I'm just here on some business.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10005500=我只是来这里办点事而已。
//[Reference] 'Won't be in your way for too long.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10005600=不会耽误你太久的。
//[Reference] 'How are you still here? Did something fail?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10005700=你怎么还在这里？失败了吗？
//[Reference] 'These teleporters sure are finicky aren't they...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10005800=这些传送仪肯定太繁琐了，是不是……
//[Reference] 'Do you want me to try and send you back again?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10005900=要我再试试送你回去吗？
//[Reference] 'Yep!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10006000=好！
//[Reference] 'No. I wanna look around.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10006100=不用了，我想四处看看。
//[Reference] 'Alright then. See you again soon.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10006200=那好吧，回见。
//[Reference] 'Are you sure?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10006300=你确定吗？
//[Reference] 'Well... come back to me when you want to leave then.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10006400=嗯……那你想离开的时候再来找我吧。
//[Reference] 'Huh... how did that not work?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10006500=嗯……怎么会没用呢？
//[Reference] 'Give me a moment to see if I can get it working.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Rem.line:10006600=稍等一下，我看看能不能修好它。
